nodes.template:
Generate a step-by-step engine mechanical diagnosis procedure.
Symptom: {{symptom}}
Flight Phase: {{flightPhase}}
Severity: {{severity}}
Recent Maintenance: {{recentMaintenance}}

Include:
1. Borescope inspection checklist
2. Vibration analysis parameters (N1/N2 tracking)
3. Oil analysis interpretation
4. MEL/CDL applicability
5. Estimated repair time and AOG parts list
6. Safety wire and torque verification steps

Generate an avionics LRU isolation and replacement procedure.
Symptom: {{symptom}}
Flight Phase: {{flightPhase}}
Severity: {{severity}}

Include:
1. Built-In Test Equipment (BITE) codes to pull
2. LRU swap procedure
3. Wiring continuity check if swap doesn't resolve
4. Post-replacement functional test
5. Log book entry template (Part 43 compliant)
